      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 23:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩成为美伊结束战争协议中的薄弱环节</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/19/world/middleeast/lebanon-us-iran-deal-ceasefire.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列和真主党之间的冲突曾被视为美以对伊朗战争的次要战线，现已成为结束这场战争的主要障碍之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/19/world/middleeast/lebanon-us-iran-deal-ceasefire.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 22:31:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩停火在开局不稳定后加强了美国与伊朗的停战</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/19/world/middleeast/lebanon-ceasefire-iran-truce.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期和平协议谈判原定于周五开始，但伊朗以以色列袭击黎巴嫩为由退出。外交官称，几小时后，以色列和真主党同意停止那里的战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/19/world/middleeast/lebanon-ceasefire-iran-truce.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 20:00:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
